{
  "stem": "8423.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she said, you come with me to the temple.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we take a little bundle of food for you, because I know by noon you will be hungry.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's-- that'll be enough fasting for you, half a day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she made this little thing out of a cloth napkin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She tied it, like a little hobo thing, and she put some little pastries in there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she went off around 12:00, 1 o'clock, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I asked her if I could go out, because frankly, to sit in the temple, I couldn't understand a word, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was all in Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I sat with mostly these old ladies-- because we had our own whole pew there that belonged our family, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So but at that particular time, for some reason, my parents weren't there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said, OK, I could go out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went out and I played with the other children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they all looked at me as if I was crazy when I opened this little thing, because they were all fasting.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I quickly tied it up and decided, you know, that I was going to fast too and not eat it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were very approving of that, because at first they were just walking away from me, because I was eating, you know, and they were-- as I said, much more religious in the country.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But babi knew, I guess, that we didn't do these things so much at home, so she wanted to go along with my mother's way.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But mostly, I think I just loved the children there because I learned so much from them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were so different than the children in the city.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
